{"tid":1949412,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國肺炎肆虐期間 留係屋企做乜好?","createTime":"2020-03-29T15:21:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-30T07:43:11.000Z","uid":18064,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3d918e6d12b0f3181a5c8f3d937e3656a67bb55d","tid":1949412,"uid":18064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T15:21:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">十點鳩叫回歸！！！</span></span><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iytbDOG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiytbDOG.png&h=ad1f8f49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n而家<span style=\"color: red;\">中国肺炎</span>肆虐<br />\n港共政府已經借疫情大大咁減弱左抗爭嘅溫度<br />\n又以「抗疫」為名「打壓」為實咁戒嚴<br />\n令到每家每戶都要留係屋企<br />\n鳩叫可以係唔洗聚集嘅情況下<br />\n提醒下隔籬鄰舍同啲藍屍仲有港共<br />\n大家唔係淨係掛住抗疫<br />\n其實抗爭尚未完結<br />\n所以鼓勵大家由而家開始<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">每晚十點</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">[red]鳩叫！！！</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">黑警死全家</span></span>"},{"pid":"a3682f9f9c8eae29fc5d12880ce6fbe1d3423e5d","tid":1949412,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T15:24:58.000Z","msg":"[更新版]到底大家撐唔撐港台<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1949128\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1949128</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c7b89468bdda868fbc6090f888e9cd6141b451f9","tid":1949412,"uid":318070,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T15:26:05.000Z","msg":"推唔到都推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67b16a1a2687ae291082882e43e0907b39688ebc","tid":1949412,"uid":318070,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T15:26:21.000Z","msg":"推唔到都推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f78013bf829b1d5f090787cee